{"tid":696723,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"其實講真，香港樓市真係唔會跌","createTime":"2018-06-10T11:02:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T05:00:07.000Z","uid":123335,"like":62,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"439e1bc744c3bf939c4a8bad6f9df72f3606a03d","tid":696723,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T11:02:45.000Z","msg":"個原理好簡單，因為有政府間接幫手推高樓市 <br />\n政府點幫？<br />\n政府只要唔俾個樓市爆，唔壓住d 地產商，唔大量興建居屋 <br />\n變相係間接支持緊個高樓市<br />\n<br />\n點解政府要咁做？<br />\n因為香港呢個地方只得服務業，e.g. 醫療, 商業, 法律服務<br />\n要刷經濟數據，要刷GDP打J <br />\n就一定要刷樓市 ，一定要推高個價 <br />\n<br />\n老實講<br />\n樓市玩完，香港其他產業都會都玩完 (e.g. 大量負資產, 社會動盪不安,  影響晒成個經濟大環境) <br />\n香港其他產業玩完，樓市亦會玩完 （e.g. 其他地方如新加圾d 醫療, 商業, 法律服務更高質) <br />\n<br />\n根本香港樓市就唔可以跌 <br />\n一跌就全港仆街架啦 <br />\n<br />\n代表到時你有平價樓住都冇用<br />\n果陣既香港可能已經淪陷<br />\n隨時差過深圳 <br />\nd 樓狗也不屌"},{"pid":"31784756a20a5a20a03fa537af7c62fb770baf35","tid":696723,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T11:04:51.000Z","msg":"林太咪講左囉。。。"},{"pid":"51ee3e4fa4d82c0d3d2af1954b05649e3103a2b1","tid":696723,"uid":123335,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"31784756a20a5a20a03fa537af7c62fb770baf35","tid":696723,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T11:04:51.000Z","msg":"林太咪講左囉。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T11:09:38.000Z","msg":"政府家陣個取向係搵多D 地 <br />\n然後俾地產商用黎起樓<br />\n要市民繼續買貴樓黎支持住個經濟數據 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但當然啦, 呢d 樓又係俾有錢佬買晒黎放租 <br />\n小市民就繼續捱貴租 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39570bce0bfde2c11db3d5739122c3b308bc94f4","tid":696723,"uid":30169,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T11:11:10.000Z","msg":"垃圾港"},{"pid":"f338f5439ce828a5f46d76e7a738b9586615cc54","tid":696723,"uid":123335,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"39570bce0bfde2c11db3d5739122c3b308bc94f4","tid":696723,"uid":30169,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T11:11:10.000Z","msg":"垃圾港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T11:12:34.000Z","msg":"岩呀<br />\n真係好垃圾"},{"pid":"5bcfdc4458b39e5fd732c6cedf1466f0e4d82b60","tid":696723,"uid":103799,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T12:08:22.000Z","msg":"政府責任唔係市民買唔買到樓，而係銀行體系穩健。<br />\n唔好攪到有人樓爆，負資產，銀行壞帳就得啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自由市場，買唔買到樓政府理撚得你"},{"pid":"a8745a5d78b27bf3ecf07137b27cf890566917c2","tid":696723,"uid":42921,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T13:01:18.000Z","msg":"丫媽係女人，山係石頭，海係水"},{"pid":"8a139d5ad09f0825d7cdc15ddbe46841a6ff7f70","tid":696723,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":23,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T13:30:43.000Z","msg":"1) 點解樓市仆街其他會跟住仆街？<br />\n2) 點解樓價唔可以係慢慢跌而一定要爆？<br />\n3) 點解講到政府萬能呢？點解唔可以係，政府想樓價跌，但因為佢能力有限所以搞唔跌呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對於樓主呢類近乎陰謀式嘅諗法，真係不敢苟同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身以為時事台先會見到，點知財經台都見到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9bb89e52566e320c63cf99d960b4a49e1697cec","tid":696723,"uid":12241,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"8a139d5ad09f0825d7cdc15ddbe46841a6ff7f70","tid":696723,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":23,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T13:30:43.000Z","msg":"1) 點解樓市仆街其他會跟住仆街？<br />\n2) 點解樓價唔可以係慢慢跌而一定要爆？<br />\n3) 點解講到政府萬能呢？點解唔可以係，政府想樓價跌，但因為佢能力有限所以搞唔跌呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對於樓主呢類近乎陰謀式嘅諗法，真係不敢苟同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身以為時事台先會見到，點知財經台都見到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T13:45:28.000Z","msg":"我答你第三點 因為政府高官都只不過係打份工 佢地持有既物業總值肯定比普通香港人多<br />\n唔通佢整趺個市將自己既資產減少為左服務大眾咁偉大? 政府高官都不過係打份工 幾年後任期屆滿一樣變返普通人要錢生活 做乜要將個市整趺幫自己身家減少? 唔好唸到佢地真係為社會社人民服務啦 特首都係打份工嫁炸 一日冇一人一票選特首 你都唔好唸有政府會打壓個樓市<br />\n仲有 樓市升得勁 有好多香港人覺得係好事黎 只係窮人仆街炸"},{"pid":"87563c3551701ac7c74d724e968acdd058f30b98","tid":696723,"uid":181549,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T13:47:12.000Z","msg":"刷刷刷 刷乜撚"},{"pid":"c6ec29ca54f8a542ce7408e5c1ea12d3b6df5e52","tid":696723,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T13:48:44.000Z","msg":"自住唔驚啦"},{"pid":"a33c6ee2e6f131aeefb34ba032e1f09ff8fa8651","tid":696723,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T14:07:50.000Z","msg":"唔會，等升到10萬蚊一尺，個個唔駛做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e1a5f558d34b9379224f0c6c0c9e5f4289fe45","tid":696723,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a33c6ee2e6f131aeefb34ba032e1f09ff8fa8651","tid":696723,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T14:07:50.000Z","msg":"唔會，等升到10萬蚊一尺，個個唔駛做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T14:35:42.000Z","msg":"全世界乜都唔駛搞 只要搞樓市不斷升就GDP升升升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be0f7adbd6dc3b691cfd0c3fa62c6e6300c6eb8","tid":696723,"uid":116443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9bb89e52566e320c63cf99d960b4a49e1697cec","tid":696723,"uid":12241,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"8a139d5ad09f0825d7cdc15ddbe46841a6ff7f70","tid":696723,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":23,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-